      <p class="eyebrow"><span>Patient partnership</span> Canada-wide</p>
      <h1>Your experience can shape uveal melanoma research</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">The Uveal Melanoma Patient Advisory Committee brings patients and researchers together to focus research on what matters most to people affected by uveal melanoma.</p>
      <p class="hero-summary">We are inviting people in Canada who have been diagnosed with uveal melanoma to join the committee. By sharing your perspective, you can help identify important questions, guide research priorities, and turn those priorities into practical research goals.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
